    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>If a blind creature holds this orb, that creature can see with darkvision with a range of 120 feet, but also gains light sensitivity (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 301). If a sighted creature holds this orb and holds his eyes shut for 1 minute, he gains the blinded condition until he opens his eyes (as a free action), but can see through the orb as if he were a blind creature.   By expending one use of mythic power, a creature using the eye orb can see as though using true seeing, and loses light sensitivity. These effects last for 1 minute or until he stops using the orb to see, whichever comes first.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, Mythic Crafter, darkvision, true seeing</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Mythic Adventures",
